<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1044824">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1044824/" class="title-link">接着说下去——张祥龙著《西方哲学笔记》初读</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1044824"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/klaas/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1010901-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/klaas/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">伸伸胳膊腿</span>
    </a>  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2006-05-14"
      class="main-meta">2006-05-14 12:41:39</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1044824_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  张祥龙的这本书的写法，粗看来像是札记的意思。札记而成大文章，自古有之。古有《日知录》、《梦溪笔谈》等等。近代沈有鼎先生那篇字不过数百的论易文字，堪称典范。仔细看来，其实不然。书中内容更像是西方哲学笔记高头讲章之类。如果没有猜错，张先生此书底本应该就是其西方...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">14有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1044824_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1044824_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










